name: Pisscoin Mouse Pad

International shipping included. Please DM @dgpgallerie on Instagram with shipping address. Item will ship within 5-7 days of purchase. For all other inquiries, please DM @dgpgallerie on Instagram. *Only for the first sale. Resale is subject to the Guzzler’s Oath.
